Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:28.56,OnScreen,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Hello 你好\NThank you for always coming to the game center. 感谢你总是光顾游戏中心\NMy name is Kusakabe Renji 我的名字是草壁莲司\NI'm not good at English, so I'm sorry if my sentences sound strange. 我的英语不太好 所以如果我的用句听起来很奇怪的话 我很抱歉\NThank you for the present yesterday. 谢谢你昨天的礼物\NI used it as one of my favorites. 我将它作为我最喜欢的物品使用\NYou gave me a message along with it, 随之你交给了我一条信息\Nbut did that really mean "be my lover?" 但其含义真的是“做我的爱人”吗？\NIf so, I am very flattered. 若是如此 我深感荣幸\NBut… 但是\Nwe can't become lovers. 我们不能成为爱人\NBecause I still don't know anything about you. 因为我对你尚且一无所知\NI don't even know your name. 我甚至不知道你的名字\NThat's why I prepared this notebook, 这就是我准备了这个笔记本的原因\Nbecause I'm hoping that we can get to know each other better. 因为我希望我们可以更深入地了解彼此\NI thought it would be nice to get closer to you through this... 如果通过这种方式能够更接近你的话 就再好不过了\NIt'll help me learn the language too... 同时这也能帮我学习语言\NI think? 你说呢？
